lyrics:
[Verse]
Vivienne, little girl with dreams in her sight
In her eyes, a spark shining oh so bright
A heart so pure, full of innocence and might
She's a shining star, destined to take flight

[Chorus]
Vivienne, oh Vivienne, your spirit takes flight
With every step you take, you're reaching new heights
A world of endless possibilities, you ignite
Vivienne, oh Vivienne, shine on with your light
